{"tid":976081,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【同股不同權】小米跌穿10元 神秘大戶疑狂掟三千萬貨","createTime":"2019-01-10T06:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T01:24:55.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7025d7dfd4c5f78f59dbd9163853c8ff93de9a62","tid":976081,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"【同股不同權】小米跌穿10元 神秘大戶疑狂掟三千萬貨<br />\n<br />\n小米(1810)昨日有數十億股解除禁售，股價下跌超過7%，市值跌破2400億港元。小米今早再遇沽壓，最低見9.44元，午後報9.86元，跌4.6%，成交激增至31億元，為第二大成交股份。<br />\n<br />\n今早有六宗大額沽盤，每宗成交股數皆達60萬股，成交價介乎9.5元至9.8元，每宗涉及成交額接近600萬元，合共超過3000萬元。據交易員表示，六宗成交皆出至同一證券商，有機會是同一人或機構所為。<br />\n<br />\n繼花旗、瑞士信貸和麥格理後，再有大行下調小米的目標價。高盛和中金都下調小米的目標價，分別把目標價從24元降至15.80元，以及從17元降至13.5元。"},{"pid":"bc832015e73d101b902e8af51a75f05a5f1d946c","tid":976081,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"高盛解釋，是因為中國經濟放緩，加上智能手機市場競爭加劇，華為正在攻佔小米的市場份額，令小米未來可能面臨較弱的廣告需求，對其銷售和利潤造成壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190110/59125833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59125833&d=LthhP1B6BQ%2FTlQrjY2XBYv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ef28201b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59125833&h=ea0841a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190110/59125833</a>"},{"pid":"b9b4f901123401a6b93a614bc1e319058b0f2d28","tid":976081,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b57678d7162eac9d20091cf98f49d183c49c7b6a","tid":976081,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"就上快10蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0789d01f866ea99744628f2caa4db6dba45c4fd","tid":976081,"uid":44513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T01:24:55.000Z","msg":"早知訓身買小米對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}